metadata.name: bunker, Zhao Ziming
metadata.description:
head to look at the situation on the battlefield, the small devil is under the cover of gunfire to attack them again.



"Get up, all of you, and get ready to fight. Nobody fires until I say so!" Zhao Ziming did not have time to look at Zhao Zhiguo again. He moved quickly in the trenches, deploying soldiers to their combat posts.



Zhao Zhiguo moved cautiously to the edge of the bunker and watched the new world outside.



"Grandma bear, really is a little devil! How did I come here?" Zhao Zhiguo twisted his thigh and patted his head to make sure he was not dreaming. "Where is this? What's going on?"



It took a while for Zhao Zhiguo to remember that his team was hit by a rocket on the way to the mission, followed by chaos, and woke up to this scene.
